{"tid":412284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發燒都要俾你屌","createTime":"2017-09-24T13:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T13:16:54.000Z","uid":17677,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"282478c7fab88bca5ebef7c1074a689bce308f36","tid":412284,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"咁今日原本諗住一齊出街<br />\n但唔好彩我今日發燒<br />\n我老婆屌撚哂鬼話係屋企浪費佢時間<br />\n係要星期日發燒 之後一直西鳩我臉<br />\n岩岩我仲要陪佢落街食野 我自己就食方包<br />\n各位我應該點振夫鋼好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc4b8c124b89d6f1a97050b82a7689e7e7b361b","tid":412284,"uid":75692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"用巨龍塞住佢"},{"pid":"2442bf91b3b1fd4b9657dbf198e8d5807b142d99","tid":412284,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"買糖水未"},{"pid":"dff729445a472c9e62d2b50aca58917c90022295","tid":412284,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用巨龍塞住佢</blockquote><br />\n病到扯唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105786ae4120aad2e45138b11f14b62c57884167","tid":412284,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買糖水未</blockquote><br />\n原本諗住叫我落街買架<br />\n佢話病唔使買野俾我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fe787e6bff4a2ad3dc117ce742db99b8afa847","tid":412284,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk